1687378003.text: "Similarly, incubation of aortas ex vivo with SRT1720 (50 mumol/L) prevented TNFalpha induced VCAM-1 upregulation and p65-NFkappaB phosphorylation, and decreased histone H3 acetylation (XREF_FIG), indicating that SRT1720 efficiently activates SirT1 in the aorta."
